# Simple Browser Test

Tests that browser automation works end-to-end.

## Test Steps

### Step 1: Navigate to example.com
```mcp
{
  "tool": "Playwright_navigate",
  "params": {
    "url": "https://example.com",
    "headless": true
  }
}
```

### Step 2: Take a screenshot
```mcp
{
  "tool": "Playwright_screenshot",
  "params": {
    "name": "test-page",
    "width": 800,
    "height": 600,
    "savePng": true
  }
}
```

### Step 3: Get visible text
```mcp
{
  "tool": "playwright_get_visible_text",
  "params": {}
}
```
